title: Gad - 26 July
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, International, Fast food, Take-out, Middle Eastern, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Part of a chain with locations all around the city. Gad is super cheap, Egyptian fast food. Vegans and vegetarians can order ful (foul, or fava beans), hummus, or falafel, stuffed in pita bread. Menu is in Egyptian and they speak little English.
